<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Submitting your application</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">You confirm that the information you’ve given is correct.</p>
<p class="govuk-body">You understand that the Department of Health and Social Care (DHSC):</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>can check with other organisations that the information you’ve given is correct</li>
    <li>can stop your payments and ask you to repay the money if you apply for a prepaid card illegally</li>
</ul>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Using your card</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">If you do not spend your payment within 8 weeks, your payments will be paused. You must spend the full amount for payments to start again. You will not get any payments you have missed.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">You understand that:</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>you must only use your prepaid card to <a href="”related/how-to-buy-with-prepaid-card”" target="_blank">buy eligible items (link opens in a new tab)</a></li>
    <li>you’re responsible for all spending on your prepaid card even if someone else uses it</li>
    <li>the DHSC has the right to ask retailers for receipts when you shop – to help prevent fraud </li>
</ul>
<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Lost or stolen cards</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">If your card is lost or stolen you must report it to the card provider immediately. If not you may lose some of the money left on the card.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">A small fee may be taken from your card if you request more than 4 replacement cards in a year. This is to cover costs.</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">About your personal information</h3>

<p class="govuk-body">If your circumstances or personal details change you must tell:</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>the DHSC and the Help to buy healthy food service</li>
    <li>any other benefit agencies you claim from</li>
</ul>

<p class="govuk-body">You must <a href="privacy-notice" target="_blank">read and agree to our privacy statement (link opens in a new tab)</a>. This explains what happens to your information, where it will be stored it and who it will be shared with.</p>

<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Now send your application</h3>
